Description:
FUNDS UNDER THIS AWARD ARE TO BE USED TO FACILITATE AND ADVANCE THE UNDERSTANDING OF MIGRATORY BIRD ABUNDANCE AND HABITAT RESOURCES 
ACROSS THE SOUTHEASTERN UNITED STATES.  SPECIFICALLY, THIS PROJECT WILL FACILITATE COORDINATION ACROSS STAKEHOLDERS THRU A VARIETY 
OF PLATFORMS (E.G., DEVELOPMENT OF [TABULAR AND/OR SPATIAL DATABASES, WEB PAGES, HOSTING AND/OR COORDINATION OF MEETINGS, ETC.).


THE RECIPIENT WILL:
'	COORDINATE AND SUPPORT IMPLEMENTATION OF TASKS AND ASSIGNMENTS ASSOCIATED WITH THE PROJECT;
'	ENSURE RETENTION AND RECRUITMENT OF CAPABLE TECHNICAL STAFF TO COMPLETE THE PROJECT;
'	ACQUIRE NECESSARY EQUIPMENT, PERMITS, AND RESOURCES TO COMPLETE THE PROJECT;
'	PROVIDE NECESSARY ADMINISTRATIVE SUPPORT TO IMPLEMENT AND COMPLETE THE PROJECT;
'	SUMMARIZE RESULTS AND GENERATE FINAL REPORTS;
